              "value": "<i>Deputy Sports Editor Matt Kim can be contacted at </i><a href=\"mailto:matt.kim@columbiaspectator.com\"><i>matt.kim@columbiaspectator.com</i></a><i>. Follow him on Twitter </i><a href=\"https://twitter.com/matt_kim9?lang=en\"><i>@matt_kim9</i></a><i>.</i>"
